rlm-sqlfluff-lint

Run the `sqlfluff-lint` pre-commit hook against every file
changed on the current branch since it forked from origin/main.

Equivalent to:

    pre-commit run sqlfluff-lint \
        --from-ref $(git merge-base --fork-point origin/main HEAD) \
        --to-ref HEAD

Reports SQL lint violations without modifying files. Requires a
`.pre-commit-config.yaml` in the repo that defines a `sqlfluff-
lint` hook, and an `origin/main` ref that the current branch
was forked from.

Aliases: sqlfluff_lint
